    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, you say the evidence \"overwhelmingly shows\" they are anti-competitive? isnt that a bit of a stretch? i thought a lot of economists and tech experts argued that their platforms actually help small businesses by giving them access to a huge customer base. why'd you jump to that conclusion?",
